---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Fragrant Signatures - Manual for Creating Natural Perfumes | Complete Guide"
  description="Comprehensive manual for creating natural perfumes. Learn perfumery techniques, botanical knowledge of aromatic plants and create your own fragrant signatures. 55,00 EUR with delivery."
  currentPath="/en"
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative py-16 lg:py-24">
      <!-- Animated Background -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 via-book-100 to-nature-50">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"%3E%3Cg fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"%3E%3Cg fill="%237D7FBC" fill-opacity="0.05"%3E%3Ccircle cx="30" cy="30" r="2"%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')] opacity-40"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Modern Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Left: Text Content -->
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-botanical-100 text-botanical-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
                Natural Perfumery
              </div>
              
              <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-botanical-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
                Manual for Creating Natural Perfumes
              </h1>
              
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-600 mb-2">
                55,00 €
            </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink-600 mb-6">
                includes delivery within Croatia
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-xl text-ink-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Discover the art of natural perfumery with this comprehensive guide to creating botanical fragrances.
              </p>
              
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                <a
                  href="/en/education/"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-600 to-botanical-700 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                  Education
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a
                  href="/en/order/"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                  Order Manual
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Right: Book Cover -->
            <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
              <div class="relative">
                <img 
                  src="/images/Naslovnica-ENG.jpg" 
                  alt="Fragrant Signatures - Manual for Creating Natural Perfumes" 
                  class="w-80 md:w-96 h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
                />
                
                <!-- Badge -->
                <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-accent-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-lg font-bold text-sm">
                  Available now
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-6">
          Why This Manual
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Quote Card -->
        <div class="bg-[#e8f0ff] rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-botanical-150 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
          <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-ink-800 italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "When one teaches, two learn."
          </blockquote>
          <cite class="text-lg text-botanical-700 font-semibold">Robert Heinlein</cite>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Two Column Cards -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-12">
          <!-- Left Card: About the Manual -->
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-6 text-center">
              About the Manual
            </h3>
            <div class="text-lg text-ink-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-left">
              <p>
                Among the people who appreciate natural scents, the number of those who have decided to create their own natural perfumes is growing. This very lively community is crowded with curious, highly motivated and passionately dedicated people.
              </p>
              <p>
                When I started teaching natural perfumes creation in 2005, it was a pleasant surprise to learn there is so much interest in this knowledge. In order to better respond to the expectations of the students, I was curious to find out what motivates people to attend the education and what was its final effect.
              </p>
              <p>
                This manual was created from the working materials intended for the participants of the Fragrant Signatures education. The materials have been further expanded with detailed, step-by-step descriptions of procedures in all stages of creating a natural perfume.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-accent-500">
                I hope this manual successfully serves you on the exploratory adventure of discovering and creating your fragrant signature. Smell natural, feel good!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Right Card: Why Choose Natural Perfumes -->
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-6 text-center">
              Why Choose Natural Perfumes?
            </h3>
            <div class="text-lg text-ink-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
              <p class="text-xl font-medium text-ink-800">
                Whatever stage you are at on your lifelong fragrance adventure, this beautifully written book is one to be treasured.
              </p>
              <p>
                Slobodanka's meticulous approach ensures that all aspects of natural perfumery – its origins, theoretical perspectives and practice are included – and she encourages mindfulness and creativity throughout.
              </p>
              <p>
                The guide to creating bespoke fragrances is clear and inspiring, adapting classical methods for the various forms of natural perfumes. Her extensive knowledge, experience, skill and passion shines on every page.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 p-4 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-accent-500">
                A tour de force, Fragrant Signatures is much more than a guide or a manual – it is destined to become a classic and essential text on natural and botanical perfumery.
              </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Author Quote -->
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-botanical-200">
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-ink-800 italic text-lg font-medium">
                  Jennifer Peace Rhind
                </p>
                <p class="text-ink-600 text-sm">
                  Writer, Author, Essential Oils Consultant
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1 - Introduction -->
        <a href="/en/introduction/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-nature-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-4">Introduction</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Complete introduction to the world of natural perfumes and overview of all 15 manual chapters
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Feature 2 - Manual Content -->
        <a href="/en/about-manual/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-50 to-botanical-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-100 to-accent-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-botanical-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-4">Table of Contents</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Complete overview of all 15 chapters of the manual for creating natural perfumes
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Feature 3 - Reviews -->
        <a href="/en/reviews/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-botanical-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-100 to-botanical-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-nature-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-4">Reviews</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Read reviews and testimonials from experts about the Fragrant Signatures manual
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Feature 4 - Wallpapers -->
        <a href="/en/wallpapers/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-50 to-accent-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-100 to-accent-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-nature-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-4">Wallpapers</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Download free wallpapers for desktop and mobile devices with botanical motifs
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Author Preview Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-6">
            Meet the Author
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-botanical-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Slobodanka Poštić, a nature lover and professor, is the author of several books on aromatherapy.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/en/about-author/"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            Learn More
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/slobodanka.jpg"
              alt="Slobodanka Poštić - author of Fragrant Signatures"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter/Contact Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-2xl border border-botanical-100">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-botanical-800 mb-6">
          Join the Community
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-ink-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Be part of the community of natural perfume lovers and find out the latest news about education and events
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/289513248317640"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-600 to-botanical-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
            </svg>
            Facebook Group
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/fragrant.signatures"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
            </svg>
            Instagram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

